常一兩禮拜就無人再記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e29429298d7ac3e59542a255657c12a4d3c8c71","tid":13621,"uid":35849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:10:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔收兵的娘娘？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係一直比人屈我都係娘娘收兵<br />\n但明眼人都睇到成個post係冇人(兵)(打手)幫我出過聲<br />\n相反佢個邊就有好多人不停扺毀我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf326690a0ae3c1c4dea383a4336f28ff6f9a9d","tid":13621,"uid":35849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;有無凝住d fd係背後笑柒你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇呀<br />\n我sad在有好多以偏概全嘅高登仔老屈我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n網上就算啦<br />\n除非好柒（Danny lo咁），正常一兩禮拜就無人再記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係呀我知<br />\n但真心會因為啲on9高登仔嘅言論搞到自己好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d81bf3ba1fc842ec0b1686cd30ebaf2c1c636b3","tid":13621,"uid":582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:13:57.000Z","msg":"冇人記得你就算數啦，而家又要開post講返想點？"},{"pid":"dca708f4526ac6359c83eedd73d00f97ea385be0","tid":13621,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:14:41.000Z","msg":"陸小姐？"},{"pid":"be767a6e07f0b8eb987927abaa6eb0a53cb77cbf","tid":13621,"uid":39600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:16:06.000Z","msg":"記得應該係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又想比人放返出黎？"},{"pid":"71fae22091f17d35a1c5e11077d41348a0fb9006","tid":13621,"uid":35849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:18:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇人記得你就算數啦，而家又要開post講返想點？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分享下心路歷程"},{"pid":"b47dfffd7496d023b455174470713eb6baaaaef0","tid":13621,"uid":15302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:24:39.000Z","msg":"之前都有fd比人放上高登話佢狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實作為朋友都無得點幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b0a4e3923dc06a39bf4ff134eb873021367c42","tid":13621,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:26:03.000Z","msg":"幸運星娘娘"},{"pid":"5a1b3a2499c9aaffd7b852b24e22663d6fc7d7be","tid":13621,"uid":3987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:28:50.000Z","msg":"比卡超好可愛絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/162843_d20c39c8a896a6ab39d7e04614bf8bd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F162843_d20c39c8a896a6ab39d7e04614bf8bd1.jpg&h=a163d67d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c04e223f6796e3f9a62c407b51c44c4c4da1565","tid":13621,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:37:00.000Z","msg":"收兵？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7012298c32e6bf086b3c7a26a5673bb9bdfec9e1","tid":13621,"uid":11033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:03:56.000Z","msg":"又係你濕撚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0b9cd396c9b06bc5a60c3568d3d2ea69ea77a3","tid":13621,"uid":35849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:20:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前都有fd比人放上高登話佢狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實作為朋友都無得點幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實冇得幫架<br />\n我都叫啲朋友唔好幫我<br />\n廢事比人拖落水<br />\n